Third Department,

March, 1957

(March 14, 1957) In the Matter of the Claim of Joseph Abromitis, Appellant, against Todd Shipyards et al., Respondents. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, by default, without costs. Present —Foster, P.J., Bergan, Coon, Halpern and Gibson, JJ.
